title: 172: The Costco Haul Episode (Summer '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode (Summer '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the crew combed the aisles of Costco and found 13 food finds to try for you! Finds like Mexican-style street corn from the Tattooed Chef, a super yummy chicken burger from Amylu, strawberry & cream popcorn from Popcornopolis, a snack mix from Parm Crisps, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, the perfect freezy find to help you cool off this summer! So you know what to do: Push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We had another stellar haul at one of our favorite big-box stores, COSTCO!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
